        "last_activity_date": 1494025554,
        "creation_date": 1494025554,
        "body": "<p>This is an oracle limitation, you can't pass list longer than 1000 elements. The easiest hack is to divide the list in <code>n<\/code> sublists each smaller than size 1000 and perform your query for each sublist, and merge the results.<\/p>\n",
